data.description: This charming 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom residence is a true gem, designed to provide comfort and serenity. The moment you step inside, you'll be captivated by the abundance of natural light that streams through the expansive windows, creating an airy and inviting atmosphere. The vaulted ceilings make the space feel even more open and welcoming. Master bedroom boasts a garden tub, perfect for relaxing after a long day, his-and-her vanities for added convenience, and an enclosed separate shower. Step outside onto the charming front deck and bask in the beauty of your surroundings or enjoy your morning coffee with a view. Being newly painted, with a renovated kitchen, and new flooring makes this an exceptional find! This could be your next home.
